history.p: The cantata is Nielsen's last orchestral work. It was composed during September 1930, and the fair copy was end-dated 4 October. According to a letter, Nielsen was completely absorbed with working on the composition.

bibl.author: Anne Marie Carl-Nielsen and Emil Telmányi

incipText.p: En Bølge fødte vort lyse Land
Dit Nu er kort, din Dag har hast
Hver Tid værner om sit Eje
